OL,3,CPolice urge motorcyclists to ride
OL,4,Csafely as number killed or injured
OL,5,Csoars
OL,7,FThe number of motorbike riders who
OL,8,Fhave been has risen by more than 24%
OL,9,Fin the last three years, according to
OL,10,Fpolice.
OL,12,FThe says it has stepped up patrols in
OL,13,Fa campaign to promote rider safety on
OL,14,Fhigh risk routes.
OL,16,FThe initiative comes as nearly 90
OL,17,Fmotorcyclists were killed or seriously
OL,18,Finjured in 2023.
