OL,7,FDrivers in cars and vans are also
OL,8,Fbeing asked to pay particular
OL,9,Fattention to motorbikes during their
OL,10,Fjourneys over the spring and summer
OL,11,Fmonths.
OL,13,FChief Inspector Caroline Mullen-Hurst
OL,14,Fof North Wales Police' Operational
OL,15,FSupport Services said: "Reducing
OL,16,Fcasualties on our roads remains one of
OL,17,Four top priorities. We will focus our
OL,18,Fenforcement in an attempt to reduce
OL,19,Fany further casualties and collisions
OL,20,Fby adopting a zero-tolerance approach.
