OL,3,CPolice urge motorcyclists to ride
OL,4,Csafely as number killed or injured
OL,5,Csoars
OL,7,F"We look at all motorists as part of
OL,8,Fthe Op Darwen campaign, however during
OL,9,Fthe spring and summer months,
OL,10,Fincreased focus is given to motorcycle
OL,11,Fsafety as larger numbers of
OL,12,Fmotorcyclists take their bikes out to
OL,13,Ftake advantage of the good weather and
OL,14,Ffantastic scenery we have here in
OL,15,Fnorth Wales.
OL,17,F"We want people to enjoy travelling on
OL,18,Fsome great roads here in north Wales
OL,19,Fbut not at the expense of other road
OL,20,Fusers.
