OL,3,CPolice urge motorcyclists to ride
OL,4,Csafely as number killed or injured
OL,5,Csoars
OL,7,FWe want everybody to ride and drive
OL,8,Fsafely and responsibly. Whilst the
OL,9,Fvast majority of motorists ride or
OL,10,Fdrive appropriately, we'll continue to
OL,11,Ffocus on, with a view to prosecution,
OL,12,Fthose that ride or drive dangerously,
OL,13,Fat excess speed, overtake on solid
OL,14,Fwhite lines or commit any other road
OL,15,Ftraffic offences. This includes the
OL,16,Fuse of small number plates and illegal
OL,17,Fvisors.
